{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/Google搜索到github网页/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2 id=\"验证网站是否收录\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E9%AA%8C%E8%AF%81%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E6%94%B6%E5%BD%95\" aria-label=\"验证网站是否收录 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>验证网站是否收录</h2>\n<p>打开Google，输入<code class=\"language-text\">site:https: //user.github.io/</code></p>\n<p>如果提示：<code class=\"language-text\">找不到和您查询的 site:https: //user.github.io/ 相符的内容或信息</code>。或者没有搜到自己的博客，则说明说明未被收录，需要进行以下操作。</p>\n<h2 id=\"google搜索提交\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#google%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E6%8F%90%E4%BA%A4\" aria-label=\"google搜索提交 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Google搜索提交</h2>\n<p>进入<a href=\"https://www.google.com/webmasters/tools/home?hl=zh-CN\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">提交地址</a>，登录自己的账号。</p>\n<p>在页面中输入自己的博客网址<a href=\"https://user.github.io/%EF%BC%8C%E4%BC%9A%E7%9C%8B%E8%A7%81%E5%A4%9A%E7%A7%8D%E9%AA%8C%E8%AF%81%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%82%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%60HTML%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%60%E9%AA%8C%E8%AF%81%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%82\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://user.github.io/，会看见多种验证方式。推荐使用`HTML文件`验证方式。</a></p>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/38429ea957129e9cb642af690fd75e7b/1d69c/1.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 71.62162162162163%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"img 1\" title=\"img 1\" src=\"/static/38429ea957129e9cb642af690fd75e7b/fcda8/1.png\" srcset=\"/static/38429ea957129e9cb642af690fd75e7b/12f09/1.png 148w,\n/static/38429ea957129e9cb642af690fd75e7b/e4a3f/1.png 295w,\n/static/38429ea957129e9cb642af690fd75e7b/fcda8/1.png 590w,\n/static/38429ea957129e9cb642af690fd75e7b/1d69c/1.png 750w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<p>具体操作步骤：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>点击链接，把此HTML文件下载到博客在本地的根目录下。</li>\n<li>进入Github中的博客根目录下，上传此文件。</li>\n<li>然后点击验证即可</li>\n</ul>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/e369cc111a05a6ece71f247937418894/e9c9b/2.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 127.70270270270272%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"img 2\" title=\"img 2\" src=\"/static/e369cc111a05a6ece71f247937418894/fcda8/2.png\" srcset=\"/static/e369cc111a05a6ece71f247937418894/12f09/2.png 148w,\n/static/e369cc111a05a6ece71f247937418894/e4a3f/2.png 295w,\n/static/e369cc111a05a6ece71f247937418894/fcda8/2.png 590w,\n/static/e369cc111a05a6ece71f247937418894/e9c9b/2.png 627w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<h2 id=\"sitemap的生成和提交\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#sitemap%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E5%92%8C%E6%8F%90%E4%BA%A4\" aria-label=\"sitemap的生成和提交 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Sitemap的生成和提交</h2>\n<p>站点地图(Site Map)是用来注明网站结构的文件，我们希望搜索引擎的爬虫了解我们的网站结构,以便于高效爬取内容，快速建立索引。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>点击进入 <a href=\"https://www.xml-sitemaps.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">XML-Sitemaps.com</a> 页面，输入博客地址，点击 start。</p>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/07ec140b7bb7314bec51a8bea36b1f4f/b1584/4.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 56.75675675675676%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"img 4\" title=\"img 4\" src=\"/static/07ec140b7bb7314bec51a8bea36b1f4f/fcda8/4.png\" srcset=\"/static/07ec140b7bb7314bec51a8bea36b1f4f/12f09/4.png 148w,\n/static/07ec140b7bb7314bec51a8bea36b1f4f/e4a3f/4.png 295w,\n/static/07ec140b7bb7314bec51a8bea36b1f4f/fcda8/4.png 590w,\n/static/07ec140b7bb7314bec51a8bea36b1f4f/efc66/4.png 885w,\n/static/07ec140b7bb7314bec51a8bea36b1f4f/c83ae/4.png 1180w,\n/static/07ec140b7bb7314bec51a8bea36b1f4f/b1584/4.png 1342w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n</li>\n<li>​\t下载 SITEMAP 文件sitemap.xml并将其上传到网站的根目录。</li>\n</ul>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/0e4c98bfb86f206b9e37d4b9dc2cfee4/d54e4/3.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 31.08108108108108%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"img 3\" title=\"img 3\" src=\"/static/0e4c98bfb86f206b9e37d4b9dc2cfee4/fcda8/3.png\" srcset=\"/static/0e4c98bfb86f206b9e37d4b9dc2cfee4/12f09/3.png 148w,\n/static/0e4c98bfb86f206b9e37d4b9dc2cfee4/e4a3f/3.png 295w,\n/static/0e4c98bfb86f206b9e37d4b9dc2cfee4/fcda8/3.png 590w,\n/static/0e4c98bfb86f206b9e37d4b9dc2cfee4/d54e4/3.png 747w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>在 Google Search console 中添加你的 sitemap URL。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>还是刚刚的Google Search Console网站，点击刚刚验证成功的你的网站进入控制台，在左边侧边栏“抓取”下找到“站点地图”,将<a href=\"https://xxxx.github.io/sitemap.xml%E6%8F%90%E4%BA%A4%E5%B9%B6%E5%88%B7%E6%96%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%B1%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E7%9C%8B%E5%88%B0%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E4%BA%86%E3%80%82\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://xxxx.github.io/sitemap.xml提交并刷新，就可以看到博客的网站结构了。</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/c942130d2c3bd1ec881a6d673b1ef0a7/567ac/5.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 37.83783783783784%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"img 5\" title=\"img 5\" src=\"/static/c942130d2c3bd1ec881a6d673b1ef0a7/fcda8/5.png\" srcset=\"/static/c942130d2c3bd1ec881a6d673b1ef0a7/12f09/5.png 148w,\n/static/c942130d2c3bd1ec881a6d673b1ef0a7/e4a3f/5.png 295w,\n/static/c942130d2c3bd1ec881a6d673b1ef0a7/fcda8/5.png 590w,\n/static/c942130d2c3bd1ec881a6d673b1ef0a7/efc66/5.png 885w,\n/static/c942130d2c3bd1ec881a6d673b1ef0a7/c83ae/5.png 1180w,\n/static/c942130d2c3bd1ec881a6d673b1ef0a7/567ac/5.png 1675w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<h2 id=\"手动提交google抓取\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%89%8B%E5%8A%A8%E6%8F%90%E4%BA%A4google%E6%8A%93%E5%8F%96\" aria-label=\"手动提交google抓取 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>手动提交Google抓取</h2>\n<p>等待Google抓取所需时间比较长，可以利用Google网页检查工具手动提交网址。（不是必须，等待Gooogle自行抓取也是可以的）</p>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/e5f42342d0470d1a228537d420dd20cc/7321b/6.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 45.94594594594595%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"img 6\" title=\"img 6\" src=\"/static/e5f42342d0470d1a228537d420dd20cc/fcda8/6.png\" srcset=\"/static/e5f42342d0470d1a228537d420dd20cc/12f09/6.png 148w,\n/static/e5f42342d0470d1a228537d420dd20cc/e4a3f/6.png 295w,\n/static/e5f42342d0470d1a228537d420dd20cc/fcda8/6.png 590w,\n/static/e5f42342d0470d1a228537d420dd20cc/efc66/6.png 885w,\n/static/e5f42342d0470d1a228537d420dd20cc/c83ae/6.png 1180w,\n/static/e5f42342d0470d1a228537d420dd20cc/7321b/6.png 1184w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span>","excerpt":"验证网站是否收录 打开Google，输入 如果提示：。或者没有搜到自己的博客，则说明说明未被收录，需要进行以下操作。 Google搜索提交 进入提交地址，登录自己的账号。 在页面中输入自己的博客网址https://user.github.io/，会看见多种验证方式。推荐使用`H…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/Google%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E5%88%B